, night wear, leggings, shorts, and co-ord sets for women; vests, briefs, t-shirts, infant wear, shorts, loungers, and trunks for kids; winter wear comprising thermals, hoodies, jackets, and sweatshirts; and accessories, including socks, towels and handkerchiefs, and rainsuits. It provides its products under the Frontline, Colors, Peek-A-Boo, Euro, Jon, Bumchums, Torrido, Thermocot, Rupa Rainsuit, Softline, Macroman Original, Macrowoman W-series, Macroman M-series, Femmora, Peek-A-Boo, and Footline brands. The company also generates power through a windmill; and offers contract manufacturing services. It sells its products through dealers, retail outlets, large format stores, multi-brand and exclusive brand outlets, and e-commerce. The company exports its products. Rupa & Company Limited was founded in 1968 and is based in Kolkata, India."}}